OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FActress and TV presenter Kym Marsh has
OL,8,Fsaid it "broke" her family when her
OL,9,Flate father revealed his
OL,10,F"heartbreaking" prostate cancer
OL,11,Fdiagnosis.
OL,13,FHer father, Dave Marsh, died aged aged
OL,14,F74 in 2024 after a three-year battle
OL,15,Fwith the disease, after it spread to
OL,16,Fother parts of his body when he put
OL,17,Foff going to the doctor during the
OL,18,Fpandemic.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@OO]rD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
