CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FFormer Coronation Street star Marsh,
OL,8,F49, has since worked to keep his
OL,9,Flegacy alive and raise awareness for
OL,10,Fprostate cancer, with her advocacy
OL,11,Femphasising how a diagnosis can be "so
OL,12,Fdevastating to a family" if it is
OL,13,Ffound too late.
OL,15,FIn an interview with the Press
OL,16,FAssociation, the actress hailed her
OL,17,Ffather as the "don of the family", and
OL,18,Fsaid: "He was only little in terms of
OL,19,Fhis height, but he had the heart of a
OL,20,Flion.
OL,26,@sD@dOUtD@XO]yD@OOUyD@aO]zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"He was just dad. He was everything to
OL,8,Feveryone ` he was brave, funny and so
OL,9,Fsupportive. He adored the bones of my
OL,10,Fmum, they were so close. They were
OL,11,Falways together."
OL,13,FMarsh said her mother, Pauline, has
OL,14,Fbeen "left devastated" since her
OL,15,Fhusband of 60 years died, and said:
OL,16,F"When we found out dad was terminally
OL,17,Fill and his cancer was incurable, it
OL,18,Fbroke us.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]vD@FOUvD@VO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"Nothing seemed to get him down. If he
OL,8,Fhad been ill, he would get back up
OL,9,Fagain. But he said to us: 'This is a
OL,10,Ffight I'm going to lose, I can't beat
OL,11,Fthis one.'
OL,13,F"That was devastating to hear him say
OL,14,Fthat, and for us to realise that was
OL,15,Freally heartbreaking."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
