PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"It's a very personal journey that we
OL,8,Fall went on with dad and for her to do
OL,9,Fthis means such a lot to us. She has
OL,10,Fgot such a good heart.
OL,12,F"We'll all be heading down there to
OL,13,Fcheer her on. She's a gorgeous girl,
OL,14,Fand I know she's gonna absolutely
OL,15,Fsmash it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
