PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FThe Whiston-born actress said her and
OL,8,Fher family raise awareness for
OL,9,Fprostate cancer as they hope to bring
OL,10,F"something positive" out of her
OL,11,Ffather's death, adding: "It is so
OL,12,Fdevastating to a family.
OL,14,F"It was devastating to us and to my
OL,15,Fdad to think that he'd left it too
OL,16,Flate. And that's something we don't
OL,17,Fwant to happen to anyone else."
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]sD@YOUvD@AOUyD@_O]
