PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777061157
OL,3,CKym Marsh says it 'broke' her family
OL,4,Cto find out about father's prostate
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FProstate Cancer UK states the
OL,8,Fcondition is the most common cancer in
OL,9,Fmen and one in eight men will receive
OL,10,Fa diagnosis in their lifetime, with
OL,11,Fthe risk increasing if you are over
OL,12,F50, black, or have a family history of
OL,13,Fthe disease.
OL,15,FProstate cancer develops slowly, so
OL,16,Fthere may be no signs for years, but
OL,17,Fsigns may include an increased need to
OL,18,Furinate, straining while urinating and
OL,19,Fa feeling that the bladder has not
OL,20,Ffully emptied, according to the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
